    "user_title": "Build Game Combat Systems",
    "value_statement": "Complex combat code can mix formulas, state updates, and logs in hard-to-test ways. This skill guides Claude, Codex, and Claude Code to separate combat calculations from workflow state changes.",
    "seo_keywords": [
      "Claude",
